<p class="lead">This program caused an invalid page fault in module</p>
<p>
The invalid page fault alert is a cryptic error caused by programs compiled for Windows 95 and 98 attempting to access restricted random-access memory. 
This is commonly an emulation and virtualization error, and often, the only solution is to run the program on real PC hardware.
Or the program might be corrupt due to antiquated antivirus removal.
</p>
