<p class="lead">NPMOD32.DLL is missing from your computer</p>
<p>
An ancient Windows program crashes with the cryptic error message.
</p>
<p>
NPMOD32.DLL is a Windows development library file designed to play older <a href="https://www.modarchive.com/">module music</a> files that were popular in the demo and music scenes. 
Sometimes coders would forget to include this file while packaging their application. 
Fortunately, we have a copy of <q>NPMOD32.DLL</q> for download. 
To use, copy the DLL file to the same directory as the application.
</p>
<ul><li><a href="/f/a53f43">NPMOD32.DLL</a></li></ul>
